        ## Overview
        
        > + **AirSpider** is a high-performance asynchronous crawler framework for developers 
        > + Based on Redis: task distribution, task deduplication, and distributed â˜ï¸
        
        ## Requirements
        
        - Python 3.6
        - Works on Linux, Windows, macOS
        
        ## Features
        
        +  Quick to Start
        +  Low Coupling 
        +  High Cohesion 
        +  Easy Expansion
        +  Orderly Workflow 
        
        ## Installation
        
        ``` shell
        # For Linux && MacOS
        pip3 install airspider
        
        
        # For Windows
        pip3 install airspider
        
        
        ```
        
